title: Karajan-Live in Osaka 1984 (VIDEO_TS)
description:
Herbert von Karajan / Berliner Philharmoniker
LIVE IN OSAKA 1984

File format: VIDEO_TS folder (VOB files)
Video: MPEG-2
Audio: 48k PCM stereo
Menu languages: combined English/German/Italian/Japanese (main language: Japanese)
Subtitles: none
Bonus: Karajan bio in Japanese
Region code: 0 (1-8); originally 2

This DVD is available in Japan only. Karajan and the BPO perform live in Symphony Hall in Osaka, Japan on 18 October 1984. The program is:

Mozart, Divertimento No. 15 in B-flat major, K. 287 (271H)
R. Strauss, Don Juan, op. 20
Respighi, Pini di Roma (Pines of Rome)
